'''Sapphires''' are blue [[gems]] used in [[Crafting]] and [[Fletching]]. Sapphires can be cut from [[uncut sapphire]]s with level 20 Crafting by using a [[chisel]], granting 50 experience. When used with a [[furnace]] and [[jewellery]] [[mould]], they can be used to make sapphire jewellery.

